  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they rolled it so tight with strings under.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had to put it in my rectum.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This how I was carrying the certificate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I would come to Lodz, I will get the certificate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I did that-- what my father said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I think it was already Sunday morning, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went direct through the highway-- I didn't go through the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I saw shortly-- I don't remember the city where it was-- an old Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was very slippery, and she was maybe 60 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told her, [NON-ENGLISH], you can hold on my arm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will help you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went through the-- like nothing-- through the-- you know, when they have those-- I don't remember what it called.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They opened the thing, and-- and I think that the German-- the woman was going to church.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I thought-- yeah, Tuszyn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now I remember the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had to go to Tuszyn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the church was between [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Srotzk ?] and Tuszyn on the other side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she said she's going to church.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I told her I will help you go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, when I was on the other side, I went to the railroad station in Tuszyn, and I went to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when I came to Lodz, to the place that-- there were supposed to be money, because-- German marks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I had to pay for whatever we were owning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Jewish-- our neighbor who was supposed to leave their money, didn't leave any money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there I was with my paper, illegal in-- in Tuszyn, which was already on the German the [NON-ENGLISH] they were called it.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
